1
00:00:05,130 --> 00:00:06,360
Why don't I

2
00:00:07,520 --> 00:00:08,850
just quit the group?

3
00:00:10,970 --> 00:00:12,500
Don't say things like that.

4
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,720
Thanks to you,

5
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:22,410
I realized that I wasn't lonely.

6
00:00:22,620 --> 00:00:25,080
Wonder-X is Wonder-X

7
00:00:25,210 --> 00:00:27,270
because the three of us are together.

8
00:00:28,190 --> 00:00:30,460
I want to tell our fans

9
00:00:30,650 --> 00:00:32,570
and the reporters personally

10
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:35,010
how much Jung Ji-eun loves

11
00:00:35,230 --> 00:00:36,630
the stage and music.

12
00:01:16,590 --> 00:01:25,460
[0 hours before the press conference]

13
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:36,310
First of all,

14
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:40,100
I'd like to thank you all
for attending this press conference.

15
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,729
Today's press conference

16
00:01:43,190 --> 00:01:45,009
is held in light of the recent rumors

17
00:01:45,009 --> 00:01:47,970
surrounding Wonder-X members.

18
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:50,590
Raise your hand
if you have a question.

19
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:09,449
Hello.

20
00:02:09,449 --> 00:02:12,100
I'm Kang Yebin, the leader of Wonder-X.

21
00:02:17,490 --> 00:02:18,790
Ms. Kang Yebin.

22
00:02:19,380 --> 00:02:20,380
Yes.

23
00:02:21,350 --> 00:02:24,810
What do you think
about the rumors going around

24
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:26,890
about how Jung Ji-eun

25
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:30,780
joined Wonder-X through her connections
with the management

26
00:02:30,780 --> 00:02:32,420
of her previous agency?

27
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:35,420
Is it true?

28
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,310
It's not true.

29
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:40,320
The rumors about Jung Ji-eun

30
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,190
are all fake.

31
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:54,230
But there is evidence
going around social media:

32
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:56,340
a blurry email screenshot

33
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:59,350
and the chat records
of the former company's higher-ups.

34
00:02:59,350 --> 00:03:01,550
There are even photos of them
meeting late at night.

35
00:03:01,550 --> 00:03:02,880
How do you explain that?

36
00:03:03,570 --> 00:03:06,540
Those are fabricated
and maliciously edited.

37
00:03:07,650 --> 00:03:11,510
The email was blurred, and only parts
of the conversation were shown.

38
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:13,370
On top of that, that photo

39
00:03:13,450 --> 00:03:15,850
was taken a few years ago

40
00:03:16,050 --> 00:03:18,110
where Jung Ji-eun worked part-time.

41
00:03:20,890 --> 00:03:22,550
Our company

42
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:25,250
will gather
all the evidence through a lawyer

43
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:28,360
and take legal measures
against the attacks

44
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,360
on Jung Ji-eun and her social media.

45
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:37,579
Even if the evidence is fake,

46
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:40,350
but Jung Ji-eun entered the group

47
00:03:40,350 --> 00:03:42,980
as an exception, right?

48
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,540
Why her?

49
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:50,700
Let me tell you what happened
when I first met her

50
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:52,440
3 months ago.

51
00:03:53,270 --> 00:03:56,730
She was carrying a tattered bag
and wearing a washed out shirt,

52
00:03:57,050 --> 00:03:59,550
trembling in front of the practice room.

53
00:04:00,290 --> 00:04:01,480
I thought she was

54
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:04,150
a trainee who's here to kill time.

55
00:04:05,140 --> 00:04:06,780
But when she heard music,

56
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:09,290
her gaze had a complete change.

57
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:12,900
That gaze is not something
you can buy with money.

58
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:15,700
Through her eyes, I understood

59
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,390
how much she loves music

60
00:04:17,579 --> 00:04:19,620
and yearns for the stage.

61
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,610
You mean she's talented?

62
00:04:26,730 --> 00:04:28,710
But she can't join

63
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:30,180
just with talent, right?

64
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:33,350
She is not just talented.

65
00:04:34,409 --> 00:04:36,250
In the past 3 months,

66
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:38,180
she was always the first to arrive

67
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:40,180
and last to leave the practice room.

68
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:43,470
Evenwith bruises all over her body
and a fever of 39 degrees,

69
00:04:43,470 --> 00:04:44,950
she would overcome all difficulties
to practice—

70
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,870
that's how passionate she is.

71
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:50,110
She stayed up for 4 nights

72
00:04:50,310 --> 00:04:52,140
to choreograph

73
00:04:52,220 --> 00:04:53,870
3 parts of the new song.

74
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:58,580
Some may say she's a special case

75
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:01,550
and that she's not qualified
to stand on the stage.

76
00:05:02,220 --> 00:05:03,690
But I'm here today

77
00:05:03,690 --> 00:05:05,190
not to defend my members.

78
00:05:05,750 --> 00:05:08,240
I want to tell our fans

79
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:10,290
and the reporters personally

80
00:05:10,690 --> 00:05:12,750
how much Jung Ji-eun loves

81
00:05:13,010 --> 00:05:14,320
the stage and music.

82
00:05:17,850 --> 00:05:19,380
So cool...

83
00:05:21,610 --> 00:05:23,880
Ji-eun, do you see that?

84
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:25,990
Yebin...

85
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,360
I know.

86
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:42,800
I trust her.

87
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,650
I always trust her.

88
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:53,500
Excuse me.

89
00:05:53,659 --> 00:05:54,530
Excuse me.

90
00:05:54,740 --> 00:05:55,350
Sorry.

91
00:05:55,350 --> 00:05:55,870
Sorry.

92
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:58,130
We won't accept any more questions.

93
00:05:58,130 --> 00:05:58,650
Sorry.

94
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:45,950
Bin.

95
00:06:46,650 --> 00:06:47,150
Mm?

96
00:06:49,010 --> 00:06:50,750
You didn't have to do that.

97
00:06:52,450 --> 00:06:54,050
Why did you stand up for me?

98
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,420
I'm fine.

99
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,380
Besides,

100
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:04,670
I'm just telling the truth.

101
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:08,440
Because you are qualified
to stand on the stage.

102
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:12,100
I'm afraid

103
00:07:14,810 --> 00:07:16,380
after you stand up for me,

104
00:07:17,910 --> 00:07:19,710
your fans will be disappointed.

105
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:23,520
Your idol career is being ruined by me.

106
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:26,980
I hate that I'm ruining things for you.

107
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:30,640
I'm fine.

108
00:07:36,770 --> 00:07:37,370
Ji-eun.

109
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:40,150
I'm sorry.

110
00:07:41,770 --> 00:07:44,070
I keep tormenting and pressuring you.

111
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:50,750
No.

112
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,150
You did that

113
00:07:58,650 --> 00:08:00,380
for my own good.

114
00:08:04,220 --> 00:08:05,780
I tortured you,

115
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,420
controlled you,

116
00:08:07,770 --> 00:08:08,970
and pressured you...

117
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:14,460
because I was afraid
you'd leave me.

118
00:08:18,790 --> 00:08:20,390
But not anymore.

119
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,350
Now,

120
00:08:24,250 --> 00:08:26,050
I want to protect you.

121
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:30,970
So that you can become someone
who can

122
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:32,630
sing and dance

123
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,140
whenever you want—

124
00:08:36,820 --> 00:08:38,380
the real Jung Ji-eun.

125
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,250
Ji-eun.

126
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:56,570
You're not alone anymore.

127
00:08:59,030 --> 00:09:00,870
I'll protect you by your side.

128
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:24,740
Latest entertainment news.

129
00:09:25,090 --> 00:09:28,610
Wonder-X held a press conference today.

130
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:32,720
Leader Kang Yebin
and SE Entertainment's CEO

131
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,420
and Manager Lee Sumin,

132
00:09:34,420 --> 00:09:36,460
along with all the members attending,

133
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:39,320
made an official statement
regarding Jung Ji-eun's rumor

134
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:42,120
for the first time.

135
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:45,470
Kang Yebin stated
the team has held on until now

136
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:48,280
through their original aspirations
they held close for 10 years,

137
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:51,230
attracting the attention
of the reporters at the scene.

138
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:53,630
Wonder-X, who has been rumored
to disband—

139
00:09:53,850 --> 00:09:56,750
whether this statement
will change public opinion

140
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,090
is highly anticipated.

141
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,190
Wipe your tears.

142
00:10:04,190 --> 00:10:05,470
Those are not my tears.

143
00:10:06,430 --> 00:10:08,430
It's yours.

144
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:13,310
Stop crying.

145
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:17,850
Okay?

146
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:02,400
Bin.

147
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:04,460
Stop reading the hate comments.

148
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,730
Don't take it to heart.

149
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,520
I'm okay.

150
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:21,050
It's more interesting than I thought.

151
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:24,140
But it's a bit too much.

152
00:11:27,210 --> 00:11:28,390
It's all my fault.

153
00:11:29,310 --> 00:11:30,930
If it weren't for me,

154
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:33,910
you wouldn't have been
cursed at like this.

155
00:11:36,210 --> 00:11:37,340
It's not your fault.

156
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:40,200
Besides, even if it weren't you,

157
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:43,580
they'd find a reason to cuss at me.

158
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:46,440
Isn't this how the world is?

159
00:11:48,570 --> 00:11:49,970
In the past,

160
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:53,530
I cared a lot about hate comments.

161
00:11:54,530 --> 00:11:58,130
I'd think if what I've done
really deserved those hate comments.

162
00:11:58,530 --> 00:12:01,230
I even wanted to throw my phone away.

163
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:06,030
I blamed myself.

164
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,100
What about now?

165
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:14,540
It's... the same now.

166
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:18,620
I'd feel upset,

167
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:21,650
angry, and wronged.

168
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:26,960
Bin.

169
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:33,680
I don't want you to be cussed at.

170
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,580
I'd rather be the one cussed at,

171
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:41,460
rather than seeing you suffer.

172
00:12:41,790 --> 00:12:43,520
I want to suffer instead of you.

173
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:57,120
[Kang Yebin is rumored to have committed suicide.
Kang Yebin doesn't deserve to be on the stage.
Kang Yebin, quit the group.
Kang Yebin is being arrogant again.
Kang Yebin, don't be so arrogant.]

174
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:54,610
Stop looking.

175
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:57,220
Stop looking!

176
00:14:01,650 --> 00:14:02,400
Ji-eun.

177
00:14:04,210 --> 00:14:05,970
I want to give up everything.

178
00:14:07,730 --> 00:14:09,700
Seems like I'm just a loser.

179
00:14:11,410 --> 00:14:13,040
The stage or whatever—

180
00:14:14,780 --> 00:14:16,380
I want to give up everything.

181
00:14:44,450 --> 00:14:46,820
Kang Yebin, you crazy wench.

182
00:14:46,820 --> 00:14:48,520
Quit the group right now.

183
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,270
Dating, huh?

184
00:14:50,650 --> 00:14:52,450
We invested so much in you,

185
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:54,180
yet you and that newbie...

186
00:14:54,970 --> 00:14:56,850
How did you get my number?

187
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:00,180
This is illegal.

188
00:15:01,660 --> 00:15:04,060
You have no right to live in this world.

189
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:06,490
Look at what you've become

190
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:07,990
because of that darn Jung Ji-eun.

191
00:15:07,990 --> 00:15:09,360
Hey, wake up!

192
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:26,980
Why don't people understand?

193
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:30,550
That you worked so hard.

194
00:15:35,020 --> 00:15:36,050
Our leader.

195
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:39,940
Our team will protect you together.

196
00:15:40,780 --> 00:15:41,230
Okay?

197
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,260
Yebin.

198
00:15:48,070 --> 00:15:49,750
We can do it together.

199
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:50,400
Hmm?

200
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,180
I got it.

201
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:03,170
I'll pull myself together.

202
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:26,780
I have good news.

203
00:16:27,550 --> 00:16:29,060
The advertisement deals
that were postponed

204
00:16:29,060 --> 00:16:31,400
because of the rumor
have contacted us again,

205
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:33,600
saying they want to work with Wonder-X.

206
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,520
Really?

207
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:39,430
Weren't those deals called off?

208
00:16:39,770 --> 00:16:41,300
Why would they contact us again?

209
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:43,630
It's thanks to Yebin's press conference.

210
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:45,780
As the video spread online,

211
00:16:46,030 --> 00:16:47,760
a lot of people were moved

212
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:49,220
after listening to Yebin.

213
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:51,180
Public opinion has been reversed.

214
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:55,450
Here.

215
00:16:56,020 --> 00:16:56,750
Look at this.

216
00:16:57,210 --> 00:16:58,770
Kang Yebin is a real leader.

217
00:16:58,860 --> 00:17:01,790
Wonder-X member, Jung Ji-eun,
it's been hard on you.

218
00:17:02,170 --> 00:17:04,700
These keywords
are on the trending searches.

219
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:08,380
The hate comments have been suppressed
by the company and fans.

220
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:10,329
The various accounts
that spread fake news

221
00:17:10,329 --> 00:17:11,390
have been blocked.

222
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,770
That's great.

223
00:17:15,490 --> 00:17:17,130
Thank you, Leader.

224
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:20,589
What for?

225
00:17:20,819 --> 00:17:22,150
I just did what I should.

226
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:24,180
One more thing.

227
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:27,240
A charity organization contacted us.

228
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:30,370
They're asking for Yebin and Ji-eun

229
00:17:30,430 --> 00:17:31,830
to be their ambassadors.

230
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:32,780
Us?

231
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:33,430
Yeah.

232
00:17:33,810 --> 00:17:35,470
They said the two of you

233
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:37,070
protecting and supporting each other

234
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:38,370
on social media
left them a deep impression.

235
00:17:38,370 --> 00:17:39,340
Do you want to do it?

236
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:40,250
-Yes.
-Yes.

237
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:43,010
I'll reply to them right away.

238
00:17:44,730 --> 00:17:45,930
Oh, right. Yebin.

239
00:17:47,030 --> 00:17:47,570
Yes?

240
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:48,940
Well done

241
00:17:49,630 --> 00:17:50,620
for yesterday.

242
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:51,980
Oh...

243
00:17:58,620 --> 00:18:00,850
As a leader,
you used to be strict with others

244
00:18:00,850 --> 00:18:02,720
and with yourself.

245
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:04,640
But this time is different.

246
00:18:05,090 --> 00:18:07,360
You're responsible and empathetic.

247
00:18:08,450 --> 00:18:10,650
You know how to protect a team.

248
00:18:11,850 --> 00:18:14,310
You showed
what a real leader should be like.

249
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:15,960
Thank you.

250
00:18:28,980 --> 00:18:30,120
Yebin-unnie.

251
00:18:30,330 --> 00:18:30,700
Yes?

252
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:34,950
I want to say sorry.

253
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:41,220
I thought you only cared about Ji-eun

254
00:18:41,780 --> 00:18:43,450
and only helped her.

255
00:18:45,510 --> 00:18:47,650
I was upset for a while.

256
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:52,270
But now I understand.

257
00:18:53,620 --> 00:18:55,760
That you were also protecting me.

258
00:18:59,050 --> 00:19:00,820
You helped Ji-eun

259
00:19:01,020 --> 00:19:03,220
because you knew she was being wronged.

260
00:19:03,450 --> 00:19:05,250
You also shouldered everything

261
00:19:05,930 --> 00:19:09,330
not because you're stubborn,
but because you're the leader.

262
00:19:13,990 --> 00:19:15,150
I...

263
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:17,920
was upset thinking only for myself.

264
00:19:19,470 --> 00:19:22,330
I didn't know
how many things you were shouldering.

265
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:28,120
So I'm sorry.

266
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:29,750
Leader—

267
00:19:30,100 --> 00:19:31,270
no, Yebin-unnie.

268
00:19:34,530 --> 00:19:35,830
And thank you...

269
00:19:36,950 --> 00:19:38,410
for always protecting us.

270
00:19:41,090 --> 00:19:44,090
Thank you for protecting Wonder-X
until the very end.

271
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:48,150
Hey, you idiot.

272
00:19:48,210 --> 00:19:49,270
Why are you crying?

273
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:51,850
We're in the same team, Wonder-X.

274
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,360
Let's not talk about the past

275
00:19:55,410 --> 00:19:56,610
and prepare for the performance instead.

276
00:19:56,610 --> 00:19:57,260
What do you think?

277
00:19:57,260 --> 00:19:58,060
That's right.

278
00:19:58,440 --> 00:19:59,640
Let's do it together.

279
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,040
We are Wonder-X's

280
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:02,830
Jung Ji-eun!

281
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,060
Kang Yebin!

282
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:05,780
Song Minah!

283
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,230
1, 2, 3.

284
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:08,620
Let's go!

285
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:10,930
Let's work hard.

286
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:13,740
I'm so happy.

287
00:20:13,740 --> 00:20:14,340
Hug us.

288
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:15,440
What should I do?

289
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,320
Hug us!

290
00:20:42,810 --> 00:20:43,680
Thank you.

291
00:20:58,180 --> 00:20:59,480
It's finally over.

292
00:21:00,330 --> 00:21:03,720
It feels like
we are working even better together now.

293
00:21:04,290 --> 00:21:05,210
Yebin.

294
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:08,380
Your dance moves today
were so cool.

295
00:21:09,590 --> 00:21:10,150
Hey.

296
00:21:10,280 --> 00:21:11,820
You've improved a lot.

297
00:21:12,220 --> 00:21:14,690
Your spin improved a lot.

298
00:21:15,130 --> 00:21:15,930
That's right.

299
00:21:16,420 --> 00:21:19,420
Your facial expression
looked so natural too.

300
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:22,790
It's all thanks to you.

301
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:25,720
But Ji-eun,

302
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:27,470
your waves are seriously the best.

303
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:28,240
Teach me too.

304
00:21:28,460 --> 00:21:29,280
Okay.

305
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,480
How do I do it?

306
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:35,030
Relax your shoulders.

307
00:21:35,530 --> 00:21:37,190
Slightly bend your right side.

308
00:21:37,190 --> 00:21:39,520
1, 2, 3.

309
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,480
Oh, I see.

310
00:21:40,730 --> 00:21:41,090
Yes.

311
00:21:42,010 --> 00:21:42,930
Relax.

312
00:21:46,330 --> 00:21:47,150
Yebin.

313
00:21:48,420 --> 00:21:49,550
Come and join us.

314
00:21:50,860 --> 00:21:52,460
If we all do it together,

315
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:54,240
we'll be able to do it better.

316
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:55,580
Ah...

317
00:21:56,950 --> 00:21:57,680
Sure.

318
00:22:00,140 --> 00:22:01,420
How do you do it?

319
00:22:01,490 --> 00:22:02,900
Relax your shoulders.

320
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:04,220
Right shoulder down.

321
00:22:04,220 --> 00:22:06,080
Right shoulder down and pull it back.

322
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:07,650
Like this.

323
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:13,260
Pull it back.

324
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:14,100
Huh?

325
00:22:14,320 --> 00:22:15,520
It looks much better.

326
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,180
What?

327
00:22:20,190 --> 00:22:22,320
The two of you are leaving me out again.

328
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,880
That's too much.

329
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:25,680
What?

330
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:27,320
-No.
-Are you upset again?

331
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:29,670
Unnie's upset again.

332
00:22:29,670 --> 00:22:30,290
Unnie.

333
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:31,680
Hey, that's not true.

334
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:33,180
We're a team.

335
00:22:33,290 --> 00:22:35,610
Unnie, the three of us are a team.

336
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:37,300
Unnie!

337
00:22:37,380 --> 00:22:38,040
Seriously.

338
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:40,110
Because you always leave me out.

339
00:22:46,110 --> 00:22:49,520
[1 hour before Wonder-X's performance]

340
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:51,170
[0 hours before Wonder-X's performance]

341
00:23:12,930 --> 00:23:17,690
♪ Through the white curtains ♪

342
00:23:17,690 --> 00:23:21,760
♪ Today's sunlight shines through gently ♪

343
00:23:22,420 --> 00:23:26,750
♪ From my toes, the excitement spreads ♪

344
00:23:27,180 --> 00:23:31,320
♪ It's not as strong as it was yesterday ♪

345
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:36,350
♪ I feel awkward ♪

346
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:41,030
♪ But it's okay; I can just be pretty ♪

347
00:23:41,180 --> 00:23:45,580
♪ The trembling of my fingers ♪

348
00:23:45,580 --> 00:23:49,880
♪ I hold my breath and call your name ♪

349
00:23:50,250 --> 00:23:52,650
♪ Right now, we are like the moment ♪

350
00:23:52,650 --> 00:23:55,150
♪ The first page was revealed ♪

351
00:23:55,150 --> 00:23:57,600
♪ My thoughts I wrote carefully ♪

352
00:23:57,600 --> 00:24:00,350
♪ I'll hold it tight,
so it won't get tainted ♪

353
00:24:00,350 --> 00:24:02,480
♪ It's okay not to run ♪

354
00:24:02,520 --> 00:24:04,750
♪ I will collect these days word by word ♪

355
00:24:04,750 --> 00:24:06,720
♪ Even the insignificant gaze ♪

356
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:10,020
♪ I want to keep it in my heart forever ♪

357
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:21,950
♪ Walking on the street
with you in school uniform ♪

358
00:24:21,950 --> 00:24:26,450
♪ The small footsteps
that we walk together in sync ♪

359
00:24:26,620 --> 00:24:31,620
♪ When you chatter away,
then suddenly stop ♪

360
00:24:31,620 --> 00:24:35,950
♪ I remember you were always smiling ♪

361
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:40,550
♪ When I say something clumsy ♪

362
00:24:40,550 --> 00:24:45,970
♪ You would smile
and nod your head gently ♪

363
00:24:45,970 --> 00:24:48,400
♪ Even if we don't know each other well ♪

364
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,320
♪ We became more and more alike ♪

365
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:54,750
♪ The wind blows past our feelings ♪

366
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:57,310
♪ Right now, we are like the moment ♪

367
00:24:57,310 --> 00:24:59,680
♪ The first page was opened ♪

368
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:02,220
♪ My thoughts I wrote carefully ♪

369
00:25:02,220 --> 00:25:05,020
♪ I'll hold it tight
so it won't get tainted ♪

370
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:07,220
♪ It's okay not to run ♪

371
00:25:07,220 --> 00:25:09,420
♪ I will collect these days word by word ♪

372
00:25:09,930 --> 00:25:12,750
Wonder-X, you're the best!

373
00:25:12,750 --> 00:25:14,030
The best!

374
00:25:17,780 --> 00:25:22,650
♪ I'm afraid tomorrow will be different ♪

375
00:25:22,650 --> 00:25:27,250
♪ I'm a little scared, but I won't stop ♪

376
00:25:27,250 --> 00:25:31,980
♪ I'll say it proudly by your side ♪

377
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:34,350
♪ I wish it could ♪

378
00:25:35,650 --> 00:25:40,780
♪ Stay just like this ♪

379
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:43,360
♪ For the moment ♪

380
00:25:43,360 --> 00:25:45,820
♪ We flip open our first page ♪

381
00:25:45,820 --> 00:25:48,230
♪ I want to write down ♪

382
00:25:48,230 --> 00:25:51,050
♪ The truest feelings of my heart ♪

383
00:25:51,050 --> 00:25:53,560
♪ I don't know who you are,
but you feel familiar ♪

384
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:57,220
♪ When you cry,
I will be in front of you ♪

385
00:25:57,220 --> 00:25:59,080
♪ Because together we are ♪

386
00:25:59,080 --> 00:26:01,750
Thank you for coming

387
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,520
to watch our performance.

388
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:07,450
Actually, we went through a lot.

389
00:26:08,050 --> 00:26:10,980
We went through tiring
and upsetting times.

390
00:26:11,910 --> 00:26:14,880
But thanks to all of you,

391
00:26:14,950 --> 00:26:16,870
we could be here today.

392
00:26:16,870 --> 00:26:18,450
Thank you.

393
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:20,300
Also,

394
00:26:20,620 --> 00:26:22,050
Ji-eun and Minah,

395
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,940
with you beside me

396
00:26:23,940 --> 00:26:26,720
I realized I'm not alone.

397
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:29,950
Wonder-X is Wonder-X

398
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:32,000
because the 3 of us are together.

399
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,120
Thank you.

400
00:26:36,090 --> 00:26:37,650
Thank you!

401
00:26:40,380 --> 00:26:43,480
I wasn't good enough before

402
00:26:44,620 --> 00:26:46,780
and I was afraid to go on stage.

403
00:26:50,950 --> 00:26:53,880
But thanks to the fans

404
00:26:55,350 --> 00:26:57,950
and Yebin and Minah...

405
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:01,480
I could achieve what I can today.

406
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:03,640
I'm so happy right now.

407
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:06,420
I'm very happy to have joined Wonder-X.

408
00:27:07,730 --> 00:27:09,830
Thank you!

409
00:27:12,490 --> 00:27:13,420
Me too.

410
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:17,450
I used to be sensitive
and would be sad by myself.

411
00:27:18,490 --> 00:27:20,550
I used to throw tantrums at Yebin too.

412
00:27:22,290 --> 00:27:23,750
When I think about those times,

413
00:27:23,750 --> 00:27:25,690
I feel so immature.

414
00:27:26,610 --> 00:27:28,550
Yebin, who always protected me,

415
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:31,680
Ji-eun, who always indulged me,

416
00:27:33,420 --> 00:27:35,420
and to the fans who trust us,

417
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:37,650
thank you so much.

418
00:27:38,390 --> 00:27:40,190
I'll work hard in the future too.

419
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:43,400
Please look forward to it. Thank you.

420
00:27:45,820 --> 00:27:47,480
How was my performance today?

421
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:48,790
Not bad, right?

422
00:27:49,780 --> 00:27:50,710
No compliments?

423
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:52,510
Well...

424
00:27:53,430 --> 00:27:54,550
A kiss?

425
00:27:55,270 --> 00:27:56,250
Really?

426
00:27:57,370 --> 00:27:57,970
No.

427
00:27:59,740 --> 00:28:01,340
Do you love me?

428
00:28:05,260 --> 00:28:06,350
Of course.

429
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:08,860
I love you, Wonder-X.
